Command list
pext      : Get external pressure
pint      : Get internal vacuum
ui        : Get voltage/current
act       : Test actuators
fillb     : Pump until filling the bladder
bpopen    : Open bypass
bpclose   : Close bypass
date      : Get date
gps       : GPS synchronization
gsm       : GSM transfer
ls        : List files
cp        : Copy file or directory content on the desktop
rm        : Remove a file
h         : Print command list
q         : Quit
reload    : Reload test mode timeout for a defined time (reload 120m)
available : Display remaining time on test mode

GSM commands
gsm_gps_on       : GSM and GPS on
gsm_gps_off      : GSM and GPS off
gsm_setup_pilot  : Setup GSM for pilot (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_setup_acq    : Setup GSM for acquisition (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_sim          : Unlock SIM card (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_data_con     : Launch data connection (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_setup_ftp    : Configure ftp (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_switch_pilot : Switch for pilot (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_switch_acq   : Switch for acquisition (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_sms          : Send vitals by SMS (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_clean        : Delete all files registered in modem (only if gsm is ON)
gsm_test         : Direct access on AT commands, send "quit" to exit direct mode (only if gsm is ON)

Advanced
pumps X : pompe Xs (lent)
pumpf X : pompe Xs (rapide)
evh     : ouvre l'electrovalve 30s
bypass  : ouvre le bypass 30s
dvmine  : deverminage de la carte
nominal : mode nominal pour mesure de conso
cychydr : test du circuit hydraulique
mkdir   : creer un repertoire
mv      : deplacer un fichier
ps      : liste les processus

Set params
stage   : Stage settings
buoy    : Buoy settings
p2t     : Pressure sensor settings
upload  : On/Off Irid transfer
sys     : System param settings
feature : Special features settings

Acquisition card commands
aii STATE:X,X,X : Modify current buoy state (POSITION,NOISE,GSM)
aii PWON        : Power on acquisition card
aii PWOFF       : Power off acquisition car
aii DIVE:XX     : Simulate dive during XX time (Ex: 20m,40m,1h,4h,1j)
